metadata.name: Little Traveler
metadata.description:
In the early days, mythologies and rumors were created of a beast that bore three heads pertaining to three different Primal species. 

The creature known as Cerberus was also rumored to be stories high and hidden deep below the earth. With some speculating part of the earth was even made of them.

Little Traveler contains the beast from mythologies, with a small traveler stumbling upon the beast down in the deep dark. 

Each Original Bidder received a Stamp for their bids on these pieces:
https://opensea.io/collection/perkonstamps
